{"tid":2164470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【命中注定】28歲當實習老師遇小五女生　「師生戀」18年後開花結果步入婚姻","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T20:07:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c72eaa21da7d4057ab95dabd54fdec7da60c00a5","tid":2164470,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"所謂「緣份天注定」，台灣一名男子近日分享他與未婚妻的相識經歷，引來網民極大迴響。原來他28歲當實習老師時，遇上當時仍是小五女生的未婚妻，18年後他們這段「師生戀」終於開花結果，今年步入婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n該名台灣男子林天福上周五（14日）於facebook發帖，寫道︰<br />\n&quot;2002年我在我家這邊的瑞塘國小實習，當時我28，她小五。<br />\n彷彿就像是專程去認識她一樣。今年我們結婚。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n相隔18年師生終成夫妻<br />\n寥寥數語已交代了他與未婚妻葉懷奇妙的相遇，算一算他現年46歲，2002年28歲的他在一間小學任職實習老師，當時遇到11歲小五女生。當年的小五女生正是即將與他共偕連理的29歲未婚妻。<br />\n<br />\n他在帖文附上一張照片，他與未婚妻回到18年前相識的小學，在「桃園市楊梅區瑞塘國民小學」拍攝結婚照，穿上禮服的他與披上婚紗的未婚妻並肩而坐，未婚妻輕挽著他，二人面上都堆滿幸福的笑容。葉懷也在facebook發帖稱，「繞了一大圈然後回到了原點」。<br />\n<br />\n朋友留言︰自己老婆自己教<br />\n帖文吸引很多親友留言恭喜，表示一對準夫妻「幸福滿滿」，讚嘆這是一段「美好的緣份」、「命中注定在一起」，更指可以把相戀故事拍成電影。有友人留言笑說，「自己的老婆自己教」、「28 VS 11，多謝哥給我一線希望」。<br />\n<br />\n林天福當年的學生、未婚妻的同學亦留言表示，「一個在台上，一個在我前方座位，緣分就是這麼奇妙」，林天福回應他沒在台上教學時，就坐在學生的右邊，還稱「我記得比你們清楚」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2725000/2728585/teacher_thumb_20200819_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2725000%2F2728585%2Fteacher_thumb_20200819_c_1024.jpg&h=d5e065ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2725000/2728585/117396349_10216433299456598_1356596439070103347_o_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2725000%2F2728585%2F117396349_10216433299456598_1356596439070103347_o_1024.jpg&h=d307cfda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad116382066ecd5e543d3db499ffd2fa067d848a","tid":2164470,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0f988435fc9401500142dc20e7780f73804fea","tid":2164470,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"11哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d7477ce4c87a56dbf97054ff428ed582123974","tid":2164470,"uid":7250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"橡膠同陳凱琳"},{"pid":"7d7cb14169436cc7b4aa91cdede7f1c3028b94fa","tid":2164470,"uid":55390,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"睇相又無乜違和感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4e15af92d93fbeadab804485aca7ed7cb9ad33","tid":2164470,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"幸褔賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474f0d4c9c03f3008944e6bf99ee7b14f6ad07e5","tid":2164470,"uid":50801,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"成功就命中注定，失敗就「房思琪的初戀樂園」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d81e8aa9cdb675ffb2ca686f15139dedcc2aa1c","tid":2164470,"uid":237487,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"做老師就用結識女友心態去教書？ 一路屌個29 歲老婆但同時諗緊11 歲嘅佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df699fd928b58673b47e5f70abf6b65fd74722a","tid":2164470,"uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"40d7477ce4c87a56dbf97054ff428ed582123974","tid":2164470,"uid":7250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"橡膠同陳凱琳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:38:55.00